%F A076049 Let b(n) = A001109(n). Then we have a pair of recursion formulas:
%F A076049 a(2n+2) = 2*a(2n+1) - a(2n) + 2*b(n+1);
%F A076049 a(2n+3) = 2*a(2n+2) - a(2n+1) + 2*b(n+2).
%F A076049 G.f.: x*(3 + 5*x - x^2 - x^3)/((1-x)*(1 - 6*x^2 + x^4)).
